    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一道耀眼的白光闪过，英雄醒了过来，看到眼前的水晶，他意识到自己必须找到其他人，恢复定居点的辉煌！人都去哪儿了？他拿起一把朴素的剑，前往最近的岛屿寻找族人......</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从无到有</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从一个几乎被遗忘的地方到一个繁荣昌盛的王国，与你的盟友一起创造辉煌。使用建筑工具打造完美据点。建造、装修和装饰您的新家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/23a5df637aec13f887f0cdc5f53d8581.poster.avif?t=1771145862\" width=608 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/23a5df637aec13f887f0cdc5f53d8581.webm?t=1771145862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/23a5df637aec13f887f0cdc5f53d8581.mp4?t=1771145862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创造你的命运</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索随机生成的岛屿。寻找宝藏、装备和幸存者。与邪恶斗争，创造美好未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/f00231f52040817317ca15a37c66baf9.poster.avif?t=1771145862\" width=608 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/f00231f52040817317ca15a37c66baf9.webm?t=1771145862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/f00231f52040817317ca15a37c66baf9.mp4?t=1771145862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >抵御风暴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造坚不可摧的防御工事并设置陷阱，抵御一波又一波无情的敌人。武装你的定居者，指挥他们作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3191740/extras/7ac7d481b78d